{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\u50cf1_EN.png?t=1739341775\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\u50cf2_EN.png?t=1739341775\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\u50cf3_EN.png?t=1739341775\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\u50cf4_EN.png?t=1739341775\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Text version introduction\uff1a</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Succession to the throne</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No one can resist the temptation of power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you will play the role of an heir to a kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the kingdom to greatness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Facing difficulties</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The continuation of the kingship is not smooth sailing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Countless difficulties are coming one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to carefully balance all aspects of the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Treasury, army, people, resources, diplomacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make a choice</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every decision you make will affect the future of your kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a wise ruler who loves his people like his own children, or one who will do anything to achieve his goals?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you like it or not, you need to make changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragr